snippet.title: Yunyun Syndrome!? Rhythm Psychosis - Official INDIE Live Expo Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Yunyun Syndrome!? Rhythm Psychosis is a rhythm adventure game developed by WSS Playground and WHO YOU. Players must navigate the nonsensical imagination of Qtie, a girl obsessed with addictive Denpa music and battling severe social anxiety. Dance and tap to the beat of the music all while uncovering the truth of Yunyun’s existence. Yunyun Syndrome!? Rhythm Psychosis is launching in 2024 for PC (Steam).

#YunYunSyndromeRhythmPsychosis #IGN #Gameplay
